et first number from userGet mathematical operation from userGet second number from userCalculate resultPrint resultAt this point, we’re ready for implementation.Implementation step 1: Outlining your main functionNow we’re ready to start implementation. The above sequences can be used to outline your main program. Don’t worry about inputs and outputs for the time being.int main()
